data.name: PoolsizeBox.ToolTip
data.value:
Allocates GPU memory to texture streaming and should be set to a portion of the GPU ram. 2GB minimum is recommended for a smooth experience with the HD Texture Pack.
- 'Infinite'= Streaming limit will be removed. Useful for in-game texture dumping and debugging, but may cause crashes.
